summary:
Inquisitive hard worker who loves people and challenges. Interested in people; right from birth. Enjoys it when customers are having a good time. Good feeling for ambiances. Easy-going, flexible and knows perfectly how to adjust. 

Other characteristics: friendly, representative, customer minded, joyful, team player, motivator, creative, communicative, full of initiative, independent, persistent, eager to learn, energetic, positive and decisive.
